OL,3,CAndy Burnham supports Summerland
OL,4,Ccampaign calling for fresh inquest
OL,5,Cinto fire
OL,7,FMayor of Greater Manchester, Andy
OL,8,FBurnham, has written to the 'Justice
OL,9,Ffor Summerland' campaign, saying he is
OL,10,F'happy to support' calls for a fresh
OL,11,Finquest into the fire.
OL,13,FPosting on social media, campaigners
OL,14,Fsaid: "We very much welcome Mr
OL,15,FBurnham's support and comments".
OL,17,FSurvivors and bereaved families have
OL,18,Fsubmitted an application for a new
OL,19,Finquest, calling on the Isle of Man
OL,20,FGovernment to take action.
