OL,7,FThe Summerland fire killed 50 people
OL,8,Fin the Isle of Man in 1973, often
OL,9,Freferred to as the island's greatest
OL,10,Ftragedy.
OL,12,FCampaigners have gathered support from
OL,13,FMPs, families of the Stardust
OL,14,Fdisaster, and a legal firm
OL,15,Frepresenting them in their fight for
OL,16,Fjustice.
OL,18,FMr Burnham was responding to an email
OL,19,Fwritten to him by Summerland survivor
OL,20,FJackie Hallam.
