OL,7,FJackie Hallam was just thirteen year's
OL,8,Fold when she was caught inside the
OL,9,Ffire.
OL,11,FShe lost her mum Lorna Norton, and
OL,12,Fbest friend Jane Tallon to the blaze.
OL,14,FThose who died were given a 'death by
OL,15,Fmisadventure' verdict, effectively
OL,16,Fplacing the blame on those who lost
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
OL,19,FThe fire was started by three young
OL,20,Fboys, playing with matches in a
OL,21,Fdisused golf kiosk.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
