OL,7,FHowever, the inquiry that followed
OL,8,Ffound bylaws had been waived to use
OL,9,Fhighly flammable building materials to
OL,10,Fsave costs.
OL,12,FStaff were also not substantially
OL,13,Ftrained to deal with a fire, and exits
OL,14,Fwere chained and padlocked.
OL,16,FThe inquiry concluded that the
OL,17,Farchitects made a number of errors
OL,18,Fwhich led to the tragedy, but 'no
OL,19,Fvillains' were singled out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
