OL,7,FAndy Burnham has been a vocal advocate
OL,8,Fof for the Hillsborough families,
OL,9,Fcampaigning with those fighting for
OL,10,Fjustice around the fatal crowd crush
OL,11,Fin 1989.
OL,13,FWhile Mr Burnham said he was 'not
OL,14,Ffamiliar' with the Summerland fire, he
OL,15,Fsaid he 'understood' the issues raised
OL,16,Fby the campaign group.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
