OL,7,FWriting to Jackie, Mr Burnham said:
OL,8,F"Sadly, the experiences and matters
OL,9,Fthat you detail are all too common
OL,10,Fbehaviours by public bodies and some
OL,11,Fpublic servants."
OL,13,FMr Burnham introduced the
OL,14,F'Hillsborough Law' to parliament in
OL,15,F2017, calling on authorities to be
OL,16,Flegally required to tell the truth
OL,17,Fafter major disasters.
