OL,7,FWhile Sir Keir Starmer had pledged to
OL,8,Fintroduce the bill by 15 April, he now
OL,9,Fsays more time is needed to achieve
OL,10,Fthe 'best version' of the law.
OL,12,FMembers of the 'Justice for
OL,13,FSummerland' campaign support this move
OL,14,Fby the Hillsborough families, and say
OL,15,Fthey hope the Isle of Man will also
OL,16,Fapply the same law.
