OL,7,FThe lawyer representing survivors and
OL,8,Fbereaved families of Summerland has
OL,9,Fsubmitted an application to the
OL,10,Fisland's attorney general, calling on
OL,11,Fthe Isle of Man to open a fresh
OL,12,Finquest into the Summerland fire.
OL,14,FDarragh Mackin said: "We say not only
OL,15,Fdoes the fresh evidence make the
OL,16,Finquest desirable, but when we have a
OL,17,Ftragedy of this size and scale, and we
OL,18,Fcontinue to have rumour and suspicion,
OL,19,Fthere needs to be an inquest."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
