OL,7,FAndy Burnham concluded by saying: "I
OL,8,Fam happy to support your campaign to
OL,9,Fpersuade the IoM Attorney General to
OL,10,Fgrant your request for a new inquest
OL,11,Fand I wish you every success."
OL,13,FCampaigners now await a decision from
OL,14,Fthe island's attorney general on
OL,15,Fwhether to hold a new inquest.
